TextEng: Who are you and what are you doing here?
Text: 당신은 누구고 여기서 뭐 하는 건가요?

TextEng: I've decided I'm just going to kill you.
Who you be and what you do here?
Why would the King want a half-orc for an advisor?
I want to ask you some questions.
You be half-orc. Half-orc be stupid. How you be advisor?
Text: 너 하프오크야. 하프오크 바보야. 어떻게 너 참모야?

TextEng: Tell me about the dragon experiments.
<StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> How can you charge me for information after I save your life?
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 제가 목숨을 구해줬는데 정보에 돈을 받을 수 있어요?

TextEng: Maybe I should cut off your tongue, since you don't seem to want to use it!
Text: 혀를 잘라버려야겠네요, 쓰고 싶은 생각이 없는 것 같으니까!

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> Me save your life! You not s'posed to charge me!
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 나 목숨 구해줬어! 돈 받으면 안 돼!

TextEng: You talk or me rip you tongue out!
Forget it, I'm out of here.
Me not spend money. Me go now.
Text: 나 돈 안 써. 나 가.

TextEng: You give me gold for getting you out!
Is there a reward for rescuing you?
